creator: C2EE
descriptionHtml:
Crosswords is a free word game in which you must reconstruct all the words of the grid.
The grids can be associated with a theme, the first and the last letter of each word are revealed, the missing letters are grouped at the bottom of your screen.

The words can be displayed horizontally, vertically and cross, when a word is found, it is validated and the groups of letters are frozen.
You can reveal letters when you are blocked.

➤ Simple, easy and addictive gameplay
➤ A new crossword experience, words to reconstruct, grids with and without themes and a random mode
➤ Small characters "Jellies" to unlock to get their levels, 4 families of Jellies and 8 characters per family
➤ Common, rare, epic and legendary chests that you can get at the end of the levels, containing special rewards
➤ Without internet connection, you can play offline, no more transportation problems
➤ 1295 levels in French / 1295 levels in English and more to come, no stopwatch, play at your own pace
➤ Train your brain and learn new words
➤ Survival mode, infinite levels with grids to be completed in a minimum of time
➤ Talent tree, to fill a maximum of survival mode grids
➤ Several themes available, choose your favorite theme
➤ Several successes to make
➤ Measure yourself against others with the ranking system
➤ Never get stuck, with the golden letter system
➤ Playable on phone and tablets
➤ Free game, you can finish it without ever spending anything
➤ Share "Words placed" with your family and friends!

Have fun !
descriptionShort: Crosswords is a word game, word reconstruction by grid
